    "CLAUDE.md": "# placeholder

Research-first team. Researcher has full internet access; developer does not.

## Agent Team

This project uses a multi-agent setup. Delegate tasks to the appropriate agent:

| Agent | When to use |
|-------|-------------|
| **orchestrator** | Coordinates research and implementation. Delegates research tasks to the researcher and coding tasks to the developer. |
| **researcher** | Finds information in documentation and on the web. Produces research reports and source summaries. |
| **planner** | Analyzes the codebase and research findings to produce an implementation plan. |
| **developer** | Implements code according to the plan. No internet access - all needed information must come from the planner or researcher. |

### Preferred workflow

For complex tasks, start with **orchestrator**: \`orchestrator -> researcher -> planner -> developer\`

For simple single-file changes, work directly without delegation.

## Security Boundaries

- Sandbox is **enabled**
- Blocked operations: Bash(rm -rf *), Bash(git push --force *), Bash(curl *), Bash(wget *), Write(.env*), Edit(.env*)
- Allowed shell commands: Bash(git status), Bash(git diff *), Bash(git add *), Bash(git commit *), Bash(npm run *), Bash(npm test *), Bash(npx *), Bash(npm install), Bash(node *)

---

*Agent configuration managed by [TeamCast](https://github.com/Katoshy/teamcast). Edit \`teamcast.yaml\` and run \`teamcast generate\` to update.*
",
  },
}
`;

